      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) reported for hemolysis index QoI; GCI < 5% on fine grid.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted on the impeller passage and volute regions. GCI for the normalised hemolysis index on the fine mesh (12.4 M cells) is 3.1%, satisfying the Gradation 2 threshold. Richardson extrapolation confirms monotonic convergence. Spatial discretisation error is adequately characterised."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
