      "rationale": "FDA GCBP bench tests conducted in a controlled flow loop at 37 °C, hematocrit 30 ± 1%, viscosity 3.2 ± 0.1 cP. All test conditions are documented in calibrated test records with traceability to NIST standards. Gradation 2 requirement met."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
