      "rationale": "Predicted relative hemolysis index compared against five bench-measured operating points. Maximum deviation is 11.4% at 2 L/min / 2500 RPM. All five predictions fall within the ±15% acceptance band. Gradation 2 output comparison criterion satisfied."
    },
